MDMX

Deadsimple Markdown Docs generator with Next.js

{`Features`}

  • {`MDX support`}
  • {`Multi Language Support`}
  • {`Header Search`}

{`Non-Features`}

  • {`No CLI command`}
  • {`No GUI`}

{`Install`}

{`$ npm i @fand/mdmx
`}

{`Why?`}

{`I tried soooooo many existing solutions, but...`}

  • {`Too complicated`}
    • {`Docusaurus`}
    • {`VuePress`}
  • {`Too simple`}
    • {`Next.js`}
    • {`Nuxt.js`}

{`So I created another one 🐹`}
